The Court Orders the Following:  Count #1. 

Imposed and Stayed Sentence of:
6 Years Imprisonment (Credit - 365 days )
3 Years of Initial Confinement
3 Years of Extended Supervision

Term of Probation: 4 Years
Conditions of Probation:
Follow through with any treatment and/or counseling recommended by Agent;
AODA Assessment and follow through with any treatment recommended;
Absolute Sobriety; Random U.A.s;
No Use or Possession of illegal controlled substances or drug paraphernalia;
Inform agent of all prescriptions;
Disclose to any physician in writing your probation conditions. 
Psychological Evaluation and follow through with any treatment recommended;
Sign Medical Release for Agent;
Seek employment;
Condition Time: 9 months Huber with NON WORKING HOURS WITH STANDARD RELEASE CONDITIONS, TREATMENT RELEASE APPROVED BY THE COURT - To commence forthwith.  After 6 months, the court may consider early relase for the remaining 3 months.  
